  "body": "## Issue\r\n\r\nTruffle debugger p command displays a group of instructions: the current instruction, 3 previous instructions and 3 upcoming instructions, see PR #4412.  This is to request that the debugger will make the numbers of previous and upcoming instructions configurable.\r\n\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): v5.4.11 does not support the group instructions display yet\r\n",
